These are Puzzles for 3x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, sprite, lemonade, mirinda
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, family, fantasy, scientific
There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, grey, blue, lilac, brown
 1. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
 3. the person drinking tea is the person who likes light-blue##1
 4. the person who likes brown is between the person watching adventure movies and the person drinking mirinda##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 9. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
10. the person watching scientific movies is the person who likes brown##1
11. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person who likes blue is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |      5      |
| Beverage         | tea    | sprite  | mirinda | iced-tea    | lemonade |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | family   | fantasy | scientific | adventure   |
| Color         | light-blue | grey | lilac  | brown | blue        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, azalea, zinnia, balloon-flower, daisy
The people have 5 different jobs:  architect, police-officer, project-manager, scientist, software-developer
City: marseilles, prague, rome, boston, hannover
 1. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
 2. the software-developer is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to boston##2
 3. the software-developer is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 5. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the police-officer##1
 6. the person who growsaconite is in the middle##1
 7. the architect is the person who growszinnia##1
 8. the police-officer is on the far left##1
 9. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
10. the software-developer is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
11. the scientist is between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to prague##2
12. the person traveling to boston is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1        |        2        |     3      |         4          |     5     |
| Flower   | balloon-flower    | azalea         | aconite | daisy        | zinnia   |
| Job     | police-officer | project-manager | scientist  | software-developer | architect |
| City   | rome       | hannover      | boston   | prague           | marseilles      |

