.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, zinnia, sunflower, aconite, dahlia
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: spy, crime, adventure, epic, disaster
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, subway, taxi, tram
 1. the person who growszinnia is the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person who growsaconite is in the middle##1
 4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
 5. the person who growsbegonia is between the person driving the helicopter and the person who growsdahlia##2
 6. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 8. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching epic movies is in an even position##4
10. the person who growssunflower is the person driving the tram##1
11. the person watching spy movies is the person driving the subway##1
12. the person driving the taxi is between the person watching crime movies and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |     5      |
| Flower    | sunflower | zinnia    | aconite   | begonia          | dahlia      |
| Movie-Genre       | adventure    | disaster | crime       | epic | spy |
| Transport   | tram     | taxi     | helicopter | bike          | subway     |

