.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-4::.
House: ranch-style, craftsman, farmhouse, futuristic, palace
5 different pets are kept: bird, cat, hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: reggae, salsa, indie, folk, metal
 1. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 2. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 3. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 5. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
 7. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 8. the owner of the cat is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is in an even position##4
10. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4
11. the ranch-style house is on the far left or far right##3
12. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |
| House   | ranch-style     | palace    | farmhouse  | futuristic | craftsman |
| Pet           | hedgehog | cat    | hamster | mouse  | bird    |
| Music-Genre     | metal      | indie | folk    | salsa    | reggae    |

