.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: d&b, indie, jazz, techno, trance
House: farmhouse, cottage, gothic-revival, craftsman, modern
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, june, april, march, november
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is the fan of trance##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
 4. the fan of trance is the craftsman house##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in december and the fan of trance##2
 6. the fan of indie is in the middle##1
 7. the farmhouse house is on the left of the cottage house##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the modern house is on the far right##1
10. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
11. the fan of techno is the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |    5    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | d&b        | indie    | jazz      | techno  |
| House   | craftsman | gothic-revival    | farmhouse | cottage | modern |
| Birthday     | june   | march | december | april      | november   |

