There are 5 different nationalities: australian, dutch, british, egyptian, chinese
There 5 different types of food: raspberry, pineapple, cranberry, radish, kale
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 2. the australian is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
 5. the british is in an odd position##4
 6. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 7. the chinese is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1
 9. the australian is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person eating radish##2
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |      3       |    4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | filmmaking   | fishing  | puzzles      | reading  | hiking   |
| Nationality   | british | australian   | chinese     | dutch | egyptian  |
| Food         | cranberry       | raspberry | radish | pineapple  | kale |

