.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, september, august, june, july
There 5 different types of food: blueberry, banana, raspberry, mango, kale
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, metal, punk, r&b, techno
 1. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
 2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person eating raspberry and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 5. the fan of r&b is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
 7. the fan of blues is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
10. the fan of punk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |       4       |      5       |
| Birthday         | february | july | june    | august | september      |
| Food           | mango | banana | blueberry | kale    | raspberry |
| Music-Genre   | r&b        | techno      | blues     | punk          | metal        |

