 3. the owner of the goat is the dannemann-smoker##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
 5. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who likes chestnut is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 8. the owner of the cat is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 9. the person who likes purple is in an odd position##4
10. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3   |    4    |       5       |
| Cigar      | dannemann  | siglo | pall-mall  | vegafina | bongani |
| Color   | purple | ivory       | chestnut | lavender | coral          |
| Pet           | goat   | frog        | cat   | mouse   | rabbit        |

