 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
10. the russian is the person who growszinnia##1
11. the japanese is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |       5        |
