 7. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 8. the person playing backgammon is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is alhambra-polo is the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3     |     4      |      5      |
