.:: Puzzle 3x5-Level-4-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, magic-tricks, skydiving, sudoku
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, iris, amaryllis, daisy, begonia
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, january, april, august, december
